      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That makes sense. So for the first part, the light-dependent reactions, could you go into more detail about what actually happens at the molecular level? Like how the sunlight actually gets turned into that ATP and NADPH? I'm having a hard time visualizing the whole process.",
